01:10:40.030 --> 01:10:42.610
You compare with higher-level
theories and you'll know.

01:10:42.610 --> 01:10:44.350
But what if it can?

01:10:44.350 --> 01:10:45.160
What if it can't?

01:10:45.160 --> 01:10:47.440
Well, then this is
perfectly reasonable

01:10:47.440 --> 01:10:51.850
to do with classical
force fields.

01:10:51.850 --> 01:10:54.170
I don't need electrons
