01:13:22.130 --> 01:13:25.100
in the atmosphere that are
blocking that part of the sun's

01:13:25.100 --> 01:13:26.210
spectrum.

01:13:26.210 --> 01:13:28.800
Isn't that pretty cool?

01:13:28.800 --> 01:13:32.210
But this red is what
